款畀自己人，廢佢一半武功。</blockquote><br />\n等啲撚頭之前仲話區議會無用</blockquote><br />\n嗰啲蠢人我無理好耐，講極都唔化"},{"pid":"dfb9916acd9cf3fa780f67e62fa199169ba3ff3d","tid":219570,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:50:04.000Z","msg":"戴耀廷 風雲計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8016d3e46767725c65de50db8c5e6bb4e7c1b751","tid":219570,"uid":35305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>光復區議會嘅一大目的，就係阻止建制派撥款畀自己人，廢佢一半武功。</blockquote><br />\n等啲撚頭之前仲話區議會無用</blockquote><br />\n嗰啲蠢人我無理好耐，講極都唔化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個時係舊登，不斷同焦土定唔知五毛辯論，講區議會掌握好多資源，投建制等於懲罰自己，結果唔夠人24小時推post勁，最鬼係依D人係選舉後消失晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a472c36136e7c89561b2a2e6f1ed69b28d6a52","tid":219570,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>光復區議會嘅一大目的，就係阻止建制派撥款畀自己人，廢佢一半武功。</blockquote><br />\n等啲撚頭之前仲話區議會無用</blockquote><br />\n嗰啲蠢人我無理好耐，講極都唔化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個時係舊登，不斷同焦土定唔知五毛辯論，講區議會掌握好多資源，投建制等於懲罰自己，結果唔夠人24小時推post勁，最鬼係依D人係選舉後消失晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅登嘅司徒老賊召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b793284bb63ec2dfe8541a824dbf632c64afadf","tid":219570,"uid":46332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:53:49.000Z","msg":"又係你呀柯生"},{"pid":"452837c7edbdb88d172d3fa06cc5e7f2946c7a09","tid":219570,"uid":35305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:04:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係你呀柯生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係咪學歷有問題果個？"},{"pid":"419951920625e125ea5b9fe855ee9806b869cc34","tid":219570,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":